= Mix_GetMusicVolume =

Query the current volume value for a music object.

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
int Mix_GetMusicVolume(Mix_Music *music);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''music'''
|the music object to query
|}

== Return Value ==

Returns volume

== Version ==

This function is available since SDL_mixer 2.6.0.

